> >>work.  So I tried re-loading psmouse module, and
> >>surprizingly, mouse started working again, but now dmesg
> >>says:
> >>
> >>input: PS2++ Logitech Wheel Mouse on isa0060/serio1
> >>
> >>(normally it's
> >>input: ImPS/2 Generic Wheel Mouse on isa0060/serio1
> >>)
> >>
